            </p>
            <hr/>
            <p>I'm Thomas, husband and father of a son. I work at <a href="http://www.bachmann.info/">Bachmann electronic GmbH</a> as a experienced technical writer with high analytical skills and technical understanding. I'm an <a href="https://www.aikido-weiler.de/">Aikidoka</a>.</p>
            <p>In my rare sparetime I like to code something. I'm a certified Java developer, but I like the concepts from Rust, so now I try to learn this amazing language.</p>
